<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>
        Bootstrap Code Preview
    </title>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-body-secondary">
        <div class="container-fluid px-5">
            <span class="navbar-brand mb-0 h1">Self Care Tracker</span>

            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav align-items-center">

                    <li class="nav-item me-3">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="home.html">セルフケア</a>
                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item me-3">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="dashboard.html">ダッシュボード</a>
                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-sm" type="button">アカウント情報</button>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <main class="container-fluid py-5">

        <section class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8 text-center pb-5 mb-4">

                <!--    セルフケアを行っているかどうかを判定する処理が必要  -->

                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">ようこそ<span class="text-primary">user-name</span>さん</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-5">本日はまだセルフケアを行っていません。早速『セルフケアを行う』から始めましょう！</p>
                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg fw-bold shadow-sm py-4 px-5" type="button">
                    セルフケアを行う
                </button>

            </div>
        </section>

        <hr class="my-5">

        <section class="row justify-content-center pt-4">
            <div class="col-lg-10 col-xl-8">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">

                    <h2 class="h3 mb-0">本日のセルフケア</h2>

                    <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="セルフケア操作">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-info text-white">総合評価</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-info text-white">入力データ</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">入力データ変更</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card p-4 text-muted bg-light">
                    データがありません。セルフケアを開始してください。
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
